high_descs: Turn left, go straight to the sink, turn right, go straight to the counter.
Take the spoon from the counter.
Turn around, go in front of the sink on the left.
Put the spoon in the green cup in the cabinet under the left sink basin.
Take the green cup from the cabinet.
Go backwards and to the right while facing the right sink basin.
Put the green cup on the right counter above the dishwasher next to the tomato.
anns.task_desc: Put a green cup with a spoon in it on a counter.

high_descs: Turn left and walk to the sink then turn right and face the counter to the left of the microwave
Pick up the spoon that is on the counter
turn around and walk to the sink
Open the cabinet under the sink and place the spoon inside the green up that is inside the cabinet.
Pick up the green cup that contains the spoon and close the cabinet
Turn to the right and walk to the counter top that is to the left of the microwave
Place the cup containing the spoon on the counter
anns.task_desc: Place a cup containing a spoon on the counter

high_descs: Turn left, move to the counter where the dishwasher is.
Pick up the spoon that is on the counter.
Turn to the left, move to the left side of the sink.
Open the cabinet below the sink, place the spoon into the container.
Pick up the container with the spoon in it.
Move to the counter that is right of the sink.
Place the container and spoon on the counter, right of the tomato.
anns.task_desc: Place a container that holds a spoon onto the counter near a tomato.
